  "3226060": {
    "name": "梦境回响",
    "steam_appid": 3226060,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >项目单人全职爆肝开发进行中，欢迎加入QQ群参与讨论：<strong>805422834 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/d009812a1de85b0e37350aa35c1a6bc9.avif?t=1760849427\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里是【概念的乐园】！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由POE发烧级粉丝打造的游戏，游戏内没有<strong>特定的技能升级</strong>，也没有<strong>固定组合套路</strong>，所有【技能】全部为基础逻辑，所有的【概念】全部为可任意组合的【积木】，如何游玩，全看玩家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来游戏还会继续更新【概念】，直到【概念乐园】的大厦建成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/3e771d58b9d48c582253afe39b796639.poster.avif?t=1760849427\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/3e771d58b9d48c582253afe39b796639.webm?t=1760849427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/0c79e41e88a12bbfba372296ba5f8072.poster.avif?t=1760849427\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/0c79e41e88a12bbfba372296ba5f8072.webm?t=1760849427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/9aaae1bc53c8ef89238353c908f3c00b.poster.avif?t=1760849427\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/9aaae1bc53c8ef89238353c908f3c00b.webm?t=1760849427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/0649546e80fabd9d39d77aaa5e2ccc26.poster.avif?t=1760849427\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/0649546e80fabd9d39d77aaa5e2ccc26.webm?t=1760849427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/b2fb1fcbcb4b7fa24cfd332586a5a153.avif?t=1760849427\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每一次探索的梦醒时分，你都可以通过记录梦境来获得【回忆】，将一些概念固定下来，在下次进入【梦境】探索时快速成型！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/5c7da208eda47aba4f426baf7d4dacb4.avif?t=1760849427\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还可以在【家】中对【回忆】进行各种装点和打磨，组合强化更强的【概念】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/ddf6f8d1b961ba833709053786078eec.avif?t=1760849427\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甚至在你离开游戏后，角色也会从“现实”中不断获取各种回忆！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在正式上线后，你甚至可以和Steam好友交换【回忆】！（敬请期待）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/3652fb013906de937cad1d4b296269dd.avif?t=1760849427\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过【梦境愿望单】来自由组建流派列表，打造专属于你的BD，然后一键分享给其他玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你的【愿望单】被其他人使用，并获得好评，那么你还可以获得额外的奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/a4143d9f44c8e1d1ed58db4cfab7fcc0.avif?t=1760849427\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/64d62dd6f2eeb1063c9e5461e4eec6bb.avif?t=1760849427\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/5c7f79f0215f6b1818862beb2630017e.avif?t=1760849427\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一个在大城市漂泊的上班族，因为工作太忙，已经没有什么常联系的朋友了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在连续又忙了不知道多少天之后，你做了个的噩梦，那是一个很黑，很空，很冷的噩梦，梦里空无一物，整个世界仿佛只剩下了你自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然后，那个迷之少女出现了，她向你讲述了一个【梦境回响】的故事，那个故事中，所有人的梦都连接在了一起……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将信将疑的醒来，模糊的记着这件事，而后，每当你入眠，便会去到那个梦中的家，她就站在那里等你，等你和她一起在【梦境回响】的世界中冒险……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras/f020a572a355d7f04e532e5a22fbd496.avif?t=1760849427\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226060/extras_big/f020a572a355d7f04e532e5a22fbd496.avif?t=1760849427 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也欢迎加入官方QQ讨论群：<strong>805422834</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
